    <textTemplates>
        <name>EscalationReminder</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hello {!$Record.Contact.FirstName},
This is a follow up email on case {!$Record.CaseNumber}. Your case is escalated to our development team for further review.
We will be in touch as soon as we have additional information to share- our next update will come in {!$Record.Account.Escalation_Reminder_Frequency__c} days. If you have additional questions or comments in the meantime, you can reply to this email or respond on the case through the Copado Community.
Thank you.
Copado Support

{!$Flow.CurrentDate}</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>EscalationReminderWithRelease</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hello {!$Record.Contact.FirstName},
This is a follow up email on case {!$Record.CaseNumber}. The development team is working on the issue now- based on their initial review, they have provided an ETA of {!PlannedReleaseDate} for the completion of their investigation.
We will be in touch as soon as we have additional information to share- our next update will come in {!$Record.Account.Escalation_Reminder_Frequency__c} days. If you have additional questions or comments in the meantime, you can reply to this email or respond on the case through the Copado Community. 
Thank you.
Copado Support


{!$Flow.CurrentDate}</text>
